{
  "_comment": [
    "Solaris MCP template. Copy this file to BOTH .mcp.json (Claude Code) and .cursor/mcp.json (Cursor).",
    "Both runtime files are gitignored (they may carry tokens); this .example stays committed.",
    "Keep the two copies identical:  uv run -m solaris.tools.mcp_sync --sync   (check drift: --check).",
    "context7 is used via its CLI (ctx7), NOT as an MCP server - the agent suggests installing it if missing.",
    "When a plugin is installed into a project, its mcps.json entries are merged into that project's MCP config.",
    "Playwright's first run downloads Chromium (~150MB); remove the entry if you do not want browser automation."
  ],
  "mcpServers": {
    "playwright": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["@playwright/mcp@latest"]
    }
  }
}
